attributes.value:
var l=$('clsa-dcs-images.RetinalScan:Measure.EYE').valueAt(
  $('clsa-dcs-images.RetinalScan:Measure.SIDE').indexOf('LEFT')).length()
var r=$('clsa-dcs-images.RetinalScan:Measure.EYE').valueAt(
  $('clsa-dcs-images.RetinalScan:Measure.SIDE').indexOf('RIGHT')).length()
var res=null  
if(!l.isNull().and(r.isNull()).value()) {
  res=newValue(
    '{filesize_left:'+
    (l.isNull().value()?'0':l.value())+
    ',filesize_right:'+
    (r.isNull().value()?'0':r.value())+
    '}', 'text')
}    
res
